				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thi%E1%BB%81m/Bi%E1%BB%87t-L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-PBU5abeflXhMMrZjEuE9Vg">Biệt Lý Nhân Phủ - 別李仁甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thi%E1%BB%81m/author-euImnp4iLisTPNWkShmsSA">Bạch Ngọc Thiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/C%E1%BB%95-%C3%BD/poem-s3x28VNwVFO_JS6LZ5Jo0w">Cổ ý - 古意</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Ho%C3%A0i-Tr%C3%A2n-th%E1%BB%8B-h%E1%BA%A1-th%E1%BB%A7-v%C3%A3n-di%E1%BB%83u-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-aWa1UHP0_J5OUbYknuh4Bw">Hoạ Hoài Trân thị hạ thủ vãn diểu nguyên vận - 和懷珍氏夏首晚眺原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-giang-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-0125BTy6UD9DFdwphA4XNA">Ký đề giang ngoại thảo đường - 寄題江外草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Ki%E1%BB%81u-c%C3%B4ng-ch%C3%BAa/Sinh-l%C3%A3o-b%E1%BB%87nh-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-0jzIpTfG7Y6dlEBDheoWJQ">Sinh lão bệnh tử - 生老病死</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Ki%E1%BB%81u-c%C3%B4ng-ch%C3%BAa/author-2s518bgzaMzt1F3criTwXQ">Lý Ngọc Kiều công chúa</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A1n/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Th%C3%A1p-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-Zjaj2RN7cDY7YEsORR6j8w">Thạch Tháp tự - 石塔寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A1n/author-fyfPhTKN3bRhgRuKoMy-4A">Bùi Đình Tán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87u-Nh%C3%A2n-ni-s%C6%B0/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%8Bch-k%E1%BB%87/poem-umr1zCoeDON3g_27FG2Wvw">Thị tịch kệ - 示寂偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87u-Nh%C3%A2n-ni-s%C6%B0/author-KoYX-BYuGWIVRhuGqBSeuQ">Diệu Nhân ni sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-3eXUWOuBCTV-7VojKdd_fw">Thương xuân kỳ 3 - 傷春其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%8Bch/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-ph%E1%BB%A5-ng%C3%A2m/poem-s7lFce4QMpsdltOIzxeCLg">Tiết phụ ngâm - 節婦吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%8Bch/author-ey1vxXPrGDaptZVsFKS1Uw">Trương Tịch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%E1%BB%91ng-Cao-B%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng/poem-_mGdr2k-nwDZHmfwkCNvdA">Tống Cao Bằng đốc đồng - 送高平督同</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
